Big Endian (Sun, C6x, C6x simulator)
  Byte order:	0 1 2 3

Little Endian (Intel, C6x emulator)
  Byte order:	3 2 1 0


To build object code in big Endian mode:
  Invoke C6x compiler with the option -me
  Invoke C6x assembler with the option -e
  Make sure the big Endian version of runtime library (rts6201e.lib) is used.

To run simulator in big Endian mode:
  Invoke C6x simulator with the option -me
